    {
      "id": "2021-r1-phys-1",
      "number": "I-A 问1",
      "topic": "接触物体的相互作用力",
      "topicTag": "力学·牛顿运动定律",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "光滑水平面上，质量 $m_A$ 的物体 A 与质量 $m_B$ 的物体 B 接触。对 A 施加水平向右的力 $F_0$，A、B 一起做等加速度运动。设 A 从 B 受到的水平力大小为 $F$，求 $F/F_0$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{m_A}{m_A+m_B}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{m_B}{m_A+m_B}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{m_A+m_B}{m_A}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{m_A+m_B}{m_B}$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2021_R1_physics/q01.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "把 A、B 看成整体可求共同加速度，再对 B 单独列式求接触力。",
        "analysis": "整体加速度为 $a=F_0/(m_A+m_B)$。B 只受 A 的推力而加速，所以接触力大小为 $m_Ba$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 求整体加速度",
            "content": "$$F_0=(m_A+m_B)a$$\n\n$$a=\\frac{F_0}{m_A+m_B}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 求接触力",
            "content": "对 B：\n\n$$F=m_Ba=m_B\\frac{F_0}{m_A+m_B}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 求比值",
            "content": "$$\\frac{F}{F_0}=\\frac{m_B}{m_A+m_B}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "② $\\dfrac{F}{F_0}=\\dfrac{m_B}{m_A+m_B}$",
        "correctOption": "②"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2021-r1-phys-2",
      "number": "I-B 问2",
      "topic": "变力冲量求末速度",
      "topicTag": "力学·冲量",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "质量 $m$ 的小物体在光滑水平面上静止。从 $t=0$ 到 $t=T$，方向一定的水平力作用在物体上，力的大小 $F$ 随时间如图变化。求 $t=T$ 时物体的速率 $v_T$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{F_0T}{4m}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{3F_0T}{8m}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{F_0T}{2m}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{5F_0T}{8m}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{3F_0T}{4m}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{7F_0T}{8m}$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2021_R1_physics/q02.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "力-时间图像的面积就是冲量。物体初速为 0，所以冲量等于末动量。",
        "analysis": "图像面积由两个三角形和一个矩形组成：$F_0T/8+F_0T/4+F_0T/4=5F_0T/8$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 求冲量",
            "content": "$$J=\\frac12F_0\\frac{T}{4}+F_0\\frac{T}{4}+\\frac12F_0\\frac{T}{2}=\\frac{5F_0T}{8}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 由冲量求速度",
            "content": "$$mv_T=J$$\n\n$$v_T=\\frac{5F_0T}{8m}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "④ $v_T=\\dfrac{5F_0T}{8m}$",
        "correctOption": "④"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2021-r1-phys-3",
      "number": "I-C 问3",
      "topic": "斜面与两侧重物的连接体",
      "topicTag": "力学·连接体",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "光滑斜面与水平面成 $30°$，斜面上质量 $2m$ 的物体两端分别通过轻绳连接质量 $m$ 和 $3m$ 的重物。释放后物体做等加速度运动，求加速度大小 $a$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{12}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{6}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{4}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{3}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{2g}{3}$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2021_R1_physics/q03.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "较重的 $3m$ 下落，斜面上的物体沿斜面向上运动，左侧 $m$ 上升。三者加速度大小相同。",
        "analysis": "设斜面物体沿斜面向上为正。左侧张力 $T_1=m(g+a)$，右侧张力 $T_2=3m(g-a)$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 左侧重物",
            "content": "$$T_1-mg=ma$$\n\n$$T_1=m(g+a)$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 右侧重物",
            "content": "$$3mg-T_2=3ma$$\n\n$$T_2=3m(g-a)$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 斜面上的物体",
            "content": "沿斜面方向：\n\n$$T_2-T_1-2mg\\sin30°=2ma$$\n\n$$3m(g-a)-m(g+a)-mg=2ma$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(4) 求加速度",
            "content": "$$mg-4ma=2ma$$\n\n$$a=\\frac{g}{6}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "② $a=\\dfrac{g}{6}$",
        "correctOption": "②"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2021-r1-phys-4",
      "number": "I-D 问4",
      "topic": "等质量一维碰撞",
      "topicTag": "力学·碰撞",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "光滑水平面上，质量均为 $1.0\\,\\mathrm{kg}$ 的 A、B 向右运动，初速度分别为 $2.0\\,\\mathrm{m/s}$ 和 $1.0\\,\\mathrm{m/s}$。碰撞后 A 的速度为 $v_A$，反发系数 $e$ 满足 $0\\le e\\le1$。求 $v_A$ 的最小值。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$0\\,\\mathrm{m/s}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$0.50\\,\\mathrm{m/s}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$1.0\\,\\mathrm{m/s}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$1.5\\,\\mathrm{m/s}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$2.0\\,\\mathrm{m/s}$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2021_R1_physics/q04.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "两物体质量相等，碰撞后 A 的速度随反发系数 $e$ 增大而减小。最小值出现在 $e=1$。",
        "analysis": "等质量一维碰撞中 $v_A'=(u_A+u_B-e(u_A-u_B))/2$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 写出 A 的末速度",
            "content": "$$v_A=\\frac{2.0+1.0-e(2.0-1.0)}{2}=\\frac{3-e}{2}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 取最小值",
            "content": "$0\\le e\\le1$，所以当 $e=1$ 时 $v_A$ 最小：\n\n$$v_{A,\\min}=\\frac{3-1}{2}=1.0\\,\\mathrm{m/s}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "③ $1.0\\,\\mathrm{m/s}$",
        "correctOption": "③"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2021-r1-phys-5",
      "number": "I-E 问5",
      "topic": "弹簧振子的动能图像",
      "topicTag": "力学·弹簧与能量",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "光滑水平面上，弹簧一端固定，另一端接小物体。把弹簧从自然长压缩 $L$ 后释放。设弹簧从自然长压缩 $x$ 时小物体的动能为 $K(x)$，判断 $K(x)$ 与 $x$ 的图像。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "图①"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "图②"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "图③"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "图④"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "图⑤"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "图⑥"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2021_R1_physics/q05.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "释放后系统机械能守恒。任意压缩量 $x$ 时，动能等于初始弹性势能减去当前弹性势能。",
        "analysis": "$K(x)=\\frac12kL^2-\frac12kx^2$，是随 $x$ 增大而减小、且向下凹的二次函数。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 机械能守恒",
            "content": "$$K(x)+\\frac12kx^2=\\frac12kL^2$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 得到函数",
            "content": "$$K(x)=\\frac12k(L^2-x^2)$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 判断图像",
            "content": "$K(0)$ 最大，$K(L)=0$，且曲线向下凹，对应图⑥。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "⑥ 图⑥",
        "correctOption": "⑥"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2021-r1-phys-6",
      "number": "I-F 问6",
      "topic": "圆锥摆张力",
      "topicTag": "力学·圆周运动",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "长为 $l$ 的轻绳一端固定在离地高 $h$ 的位置，另一端系质量 $m$ 的小物体。小物体在水平面内以角速度 $\\omega$ 做等速圆周运动。求绳的张力 $S$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$mh\\omega^2$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$ml\\omega^2$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$m\\sqrt{l^2-h^2}\\omega^2$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{mh^2\\omega^2}{l}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{ml^2\\omega^2}{h}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{m(l^2-h^2)\\omega^2}{l}$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2021_R1_physics/q06.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "圆周半径为 $r=\\sqrt{l^2-h^2}$。张力的水平分量提供向心力。",
        "analysis": "张力水平分量为 $S(r/l)$，向心力为 $mr\\omega^2$，两式相等后可约去 $r$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 水平方向列式",
            "content": "$$S\\frac{r}{l}=mr\\omega^2$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 化简",
            "content": "$$S=ml\\omega^2$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "② $S=ml\\omega^2$",
        "correctOption": "②"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2021-r1-phys-7",
      "number": "II-A 问1",
      "topic": "水和冰的热平衡",
      "topicTag": "热学·热量",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "$20°C$ 的水 $120\\,\\mathrm{g}$ 中加入 $-10°C$ 的冰 $40\\,\\mathrm{g}$，充分时间后成为 $0°C$ 的水和冰。水的比热为 $4.2\\,\\mathrm{J/(g\\cdot K)}$，冰的比热为 $2.1\\,\\mathrm{J/(g\\cdot K)}$，冰的熔解热为 $3.3\\times10^2\\,\\mathrm{J/g}$。求剩余冰的质量。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$8.0\\,\\mathrm{g}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$12\\,\\mathrm{g}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$16\\,\\mathrm{g}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$20\\,\\mathrm{g}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$24\\,\\mathrm{g}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$28\\,\\mathrm{g}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑦",
          "content": "$32\\,\\mathrm{g}$"
        }
      ],
      "solution": {
        "translation": "水降到 $0°C$ 放出的热量，先把冰从 $-10°C$ 加热到 $0°C$，剩余热量用于融化一部分冰。",
        "analysis": "水放热 $120\\times4.2\\times20=10080\\,\\mathrm{J}$。冰升温需 $40\\times2.1\\times10=840\\,\\mathrm{J}$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 水放出的热量",
            "content": "$$Q_w=120\\times4.2\\times20=10080\\,\\mathrm{J}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 冰升温需要的热量",
            "content": "$$Q_i=40\\times2.1\\times10=840\\,\\mathrm{J}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 融化的冰",
            "content": "$$Q_{\\mathrm{melt}}=10080-840=9240\\,\\mathrm{J}$$\n\n$$m=\\frac{9240}{3.3\\times10^2}=28\\,\\mathrm{g}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(4) 剩余冰",
            "content": "$$40-28=12\\,\\mathrm{g}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "② $12\\,\\mathrm{g}$",
        "correctOption": "②"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2021-r1-phys-8",
      "number": "II-B 问2",
      "topic": "定压膨胀中的外界做功",
      "topicTag": "热学·理想气体",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "一定量理想气体从压强 $p_0$、体积 $V_0$、温度 $T_0$ 的状态，在压强一定下变为绝对温度 $T(>T_0)$ 的状态。设外界对气体做的功为 $W$，求 $W$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{p_0V_0(T_0-T)}{T_0}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{p_0V_0(T-T_0)}{T_0}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{p_0V_0(T_0-T)}{T}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{p_0V_0(T-T_0)}{T}$"
        }
      ],
      "solution": {
        "translation": "定压升温时气体膨胀，气体对外做正功，所以外界对气体做功为负。",
        "analysis": "定压下 $V=V_0T/T_0$。气体对外做功 $p_0(V-V_0)=p_0V_0(T-T_0)/T_0$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 求体积变化",
            "content": "$$V=V_0\\frac{T}{T_0}$$\n\n$$\\Delta V=V_0\\frac{T-T_0}{T_0}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 外界对气体做功",
            "content": "气体对外做功为 $p_0\\Delta V$，外界对气体做功相反：\n\n$$W=-p_0\\Delta V=\\frac{p_0V_0(T_0-T)}{T_0}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "① $\\dfrac{p_0V_0(T_0-T)}{T_0}$",
        "correctOption": "①"
      }
    },
    {
